| Toggle Switch 3 | 14       |  
| Toggle Switch 4 | 27       |  
| Toggle Switch 5 | 26       |  
| Toggle Switch 6 | 25       |  
| Toggle Switch 7 | 33       |  
| Toggle Switch 8 | 32       |  
| Toggle Switch 9 | 35       |  
| LCD SDA         | 21       |  
| LCD SCL         | 22       |  
